title: Gozen 3-ji no Fukyouwaon
original_name: 午前 3 時の不協和音
sinopse:
A spin-off of the 3am Dangerous and Terrible Zone series. Features a premonition of love visiting Wajima - the salesman - along with the details of Domoto and Mano's break-up and the current lives of Momoko and Tamako.

(Source: Stiletto Heels)
